STATE of North Carolina
v.
Delwood Earl SHELLY. No. 268P15. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Nov. 5, 2015.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 30th of July 2015 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Cumberland County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

<page vol="778" reporter="S.E.2d" no="276" /> "Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th of November 2015."
